  "response": "Chatting with a stranger guy daily without being in a relationship can be enjoyable and harmless, provided that certain precautions are taken to ensure safety and comfort:\n\n1. **Respect Boundaries:** Ensure both parties respect each other's boundaries and consent.\n2. **Privacy:** Avoid sharing overly personal information or details that could compromise your safety.\n3. **Safety:** Be cautious of any red flags or behavior that makes you uncomfortable.\n4. **Intentions:** Be clear about the nature of the communication and ensure both parties are on the same page regarding your intentions.\n\nUltimately, whether it's okay depends on your comfort level and the dynamics of the communication. Regular, respectful interactions can be a positive experience. Trust your instincts, and prioritize your well-being in any situation.",
